ākhyāhi me ko bhavān ugra-rūpo  namo ’stu te deva-vara prasīda  vijñātum icchāmi bhavantam ādyaṁ  na hi prajānāmi tava pravṛttim      ākhyāhi—please explain; me—unto me; kaḥ—who; bhavān—You;
    ugra-rūpaḥ—fierce form; namaḥ astu—obeisances; te—unto You;
