Kṛṣṇa as the grandfather because He is the father of Brahmā, the first living
creature in the universe.

yadā sattve pravṛddhe tu  pralayaṁ yāti deha-bhṛt  tadottama-vidāṁ lokān  amalān pratipadyate  yadā—when; sattve—mode of goodness; pravṛddhe—in development; tu—but;
