themselves materially but to please the Supreme, is of the nature of goodness.

tasmād oṁ ity udāhṛtya  yajña-dāna-tapaḥ-kriyāḥ  pravartante vidhānoktāḥ  satataṁ brahma-vādinām  tasmāt—therefore; om—beginning with om; iti—thus; udāhṛtya—indicating;
